==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Torpedo stern
<hw>Torpedo stern</hw>. <def>A broad stern without overhang, flattened
on the bottom, used in some torpedo and fast power boats. It prevents
settling in the water at high speed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Torpedo tube</ent>⟦br⟧
